    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   <span class="b1">)</span>
   = 5613.66
   <i>kN</i>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>The equation of motion is expressed by the Duhamel′s integral</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>D</sub>
   (
   <var>t</var>
   )  =
   <span class="dvc">
    1
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
