 <h4>Elastic time history response of the structure as an MDOF system</h4>
 <p>
  Number of intermediate joints -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>n</var>
   <sub>J</sub>
   = 11
  </span>
  (odd)
 </p>
 <p>
  Length of one segment -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>Δx</var>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    <var>L</var>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    <var>n</var>
    <sub>J</sub>
    + 1
   </span>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    12
    <i>m</i>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    11 + 1
   </span>
   = 1
   <i>m</i>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  Coordinate of joint
  <var>j</var>
  -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>x</var>
   <sub>J</sub>
   (
   <var>j</var>
   )  =
   <var>Δx</var>
   ·
   <var>j</var>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  Shear forces due to unit vertical load
  <var>F</var>
  <sub>j</sub>
  = 1 at joint
  <var>j</var>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>V</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   ;
   <var>j</var>
   )  =
   <span class="dvcs">
    <span class="c3">{</span>
    <span class="dvs">
     if
     <var>x</var>
     &lt;
     <var>x</var>
     <sub>J</sub>
     (
     <var>j</var>
     ) : 1 −
     <span class="dvc">
      <var>x</var>
      <sub>J</sub>
      (
      <var>j</var>
      )
      <span class="dvl">
      </span>
      <var>L</var>
     </span>
     <br/>
     else:
     <span class="dvc">
      -
      <var>x</var>
      <sub>J</sub>
      (
      <var>j</var>
      )
      <span class="dvl">
      </span>
      <var>L</var>
     </span>
    </span>
   </span>
  </span>
 </p>
